MindCrack is a server Guude started in late 2010. It is a private (whitelisted) server. We are currently not accepting applications.

Looks like I should have waited another day, the MindCrack server seems to be back online at the time of writing this. I checked and most of what I did is still there so the server rollback wasn't too bad. Yay! =)
